HEADWORD: Sewage
<hw>Sew"age</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
contents of a sewer or drain; refuse liquids or matter carried off by
sewers</def>⟦br⟧
